{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@"},{"kind":"attribute","text":"MainActor","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadioPicker"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"Tag"},{"kind":"text","text":"> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"where"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Tag"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SH","text":"Hashable"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"],"kind":"mentions"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom radio trait."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The picker itself does no have any defined accessiiblity value, label or identifier ; it remains in the users hands to define which one will be used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"However if defined in the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioPickerData","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" the items inside the picker will have such accessibility identifiers."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","text":"Forbidden by design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" in both an error situation and a read only state."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"type":"text","text":" in both an error situation and a disabled state."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"type":"text","text":" in both a read only and a disabled state."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Code samples","type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define the elements to display in radio buttons using OUDSRadioPickerData.","    \/\/ This object has the same properties as the OUDSRadioItem,","    \/\/ and some of them are optional withdefault values set","    var someDataToPopulate: [OUDSRadioPickerData<String>] {","        [","            OUDSRadioPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_1\",","                                        label: \"Virgin Holy Lava\",","                                        extraLabel: \"Very spicy\",","                                        description: \"No alcohol, only tasty flavors\",","                                        icon: Image(systemName: \"flame\")),","","            OUDSRadioPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_2\",","                                        label: \"IPA beer\",","                                        description: \"From Brewdog company\",","                                        icon: Image(systemName: \"dog.fill\")),","","            OUDSRadioPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_3\",","                                        label: \"Mineral water\",","                                        icon: Image(systemName: \"waterbottle.fill\")),","        ]","    }","","    \/\/ Prepare the selection, with a value previously selected","    \/\/ Use the data and the binding for the picker.","    @State var selection: String = \"Choice_1\"","","    \/\/ Here the picker is vertical","    OUDSRadioPicker(selection: $selection, radios: someDataToPopulate)","","    \/\/ The picker can apply some settings to all its radio buttons.","    \/\/ It can be also horitzontal with a scroll indicator.","    \/\/ Here all the the radio buttons are in read only mode and use reversed layout.","    OUDSRadioPicker(selection: $selection,","                    radios: someDataToPopulate,","                    isReversed: true,","                    isReadOnly: true,","                    placement: .horitzontal(true))"]},{"text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"There is no online specification as this component is not an official OUDS one"}]},{"text":"Theme rendering","type":"heading","anchor":"Theme-rendering","level":2},{"text":"Orange","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioPicker_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"text":"Orange Compact","type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Compact","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioPicker_OrangeCompact"}]},{"text":"Sosh","type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioPicker_Sosh"}]},{"text":"Wireframe","type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radioPicker_Wireframe"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0.14.0"}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Since","style":"note"}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A picker allowing to expose several radio buttons and choose only one within the o